    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something dependable and clean that still has plenty of adventures left in it! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
