      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The chassis remains composed on Bilstein B6 dampers, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for effective heat dissipation. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
